有。下面给你 3 种“统一放大镜搜索框”的典型样式（都不再分裂成输入框+按钮），你可以选一种我再按你的组件库落地。

### 样式 A：左侧放大镜（最常见）
```html
<div class="search">
  <span class="icon">🔍</span>
  <input placeholder="搜索模型名称" />
</div>
```

```css
.search{
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  height:32px; padding:0 10px;
  border:1px solid #d9d9d9; border-radius:6px;
  background:#fff;
}
.search .icon{ color:#8c8c8c; font-size:14px; }
.search input{
  border:0; outline:0; width:220px; font-size:14px;
}
.search:focus-within{
  border-color:#1677ff;
  box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(22,119,255,.15);
}
```

---

### 样式 B：右侧放大镜（像“按钮”但仍是一个整体）
```html
<div class="search">
  <input placeholder="搜索模型名称" />
  <button class="iconBtn" aria-label="search">🔍</button>
</div>
```

```css
.search{
  display:flex; align-items:center;
  height:32px; width:260px;
  border:1px solid #d9d9d9; border-radius:6px; overflow:hidden;
  background:#fff;
}
.search input{ flex:1; border:0; outline:0; padding:0 10px; }
.search .iconBtn{
  width:34px; height:100%;
  border:0; border-left:1px solid #f0f0f0;
  background:#fafafa; cursor:pointer; color:#595959;
}
.search:focus-within{ border-color:#1677ff; box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(22,119,255,.15); }
```

---

### 样式 C：带清空（右侧 ×，更像组件库）
```html
<div class="search">
  <span class="icon">🔍</span>
  <input placeholder="搜索模型名称" />
  <span class="clear">×</span>
</div>
```

```css
.search{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  height:32px; width:260px; padding:0 10px;
  border:1px solid #d9d9d9; border-radius:6px; background:#fff;
}
.search .clear{ margin-left:auto; color:#bfbfbf; cursor:pointer; }
.search input{ flex:1; border:0; outline:0; }
```

如果你把你们用的组件库（AntD / Element / Naive / 自研）和你希望放在“表头里”还是“表格右上角”的位置告诉我，我可以给你一份完全匹配你当前页面风格的最终 CSS（含尺寸、圆角、hover、focus、暗色模式可选）。

下面给你一个可直接打开的**完整 HTML 页面**（含表格、数据集下拉、右上角统一放大镜搜索、分页外观），不依赖框架。把代码存成 `index.html` 双击即可运行；搜索会实时过滤“模型名称”列。

```html
<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>历史结果 - 示例</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#ffffff;
      --text:#1f2329;
      --muted:#6b7280;
      --border:#e5e7eb;
      --border2:#d9d9d9;
      --head:#f7f8fa;
      --link:#1677ff;
      --focus: rgba(22,119,255,.18);
      --shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
      --radius: 10px;
      --radius-sm: 6px;
      --row-hover:#fafafa;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "PingFang SC",
        "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;
      background:#f3f4f6;
      color:var(--text);
    }
    a{color:var(--link); text-decoration:none}
    a:hover{text-decoration:underline}

    .page{
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 22px auto;
      padding: 0 14px;
    }
    .card{
      background:var(--bg);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .header{
      padding: 16px 18px 10px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .title{
      font-size:18px;
      font-weight:700;
      margin:0 0 12px 0;
    }

    .toolbar{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:12px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }
    .field{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:13px;
    }
    select{
      height:32px;
      padding: 0 10px;
      border:1px solid var(--border2);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      background:#fff;
      outline:none;
    }
    select:focus{
      border-color: var(--link);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--focus);
    }

    /* 统一放大镜搜索框（左侧放大镜 + 清空按钮） */
    .search{
      margin-left:auto;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      height:32px;
      width: 280px;
      padding: 0 10px;
      border:1px solid var(--border2);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      background:#fff;
    }
    .search svg{ flex:0 0 auto; color:#8c8c8c }
    .search input{
      flex:1 1 auto;
      border:0;
      outline:0;
      font-size:14px;
      min-width: 0;
    }
    .clearBtn{
      border:0;
      background:transparent;
      color:#bfbfbf;
      cursor:pointer;
      font-size:18px;
      line-height:1;
      padding: 0 2px;
      display:none;
    }
    .search:focus-within{
      border-color: var(--link);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--focus);
    }

    .tableWrap{ overflow:auto; }
    table{
      width:100%;
      border-collapse:separate;
      border-spacing:0;
      table-layout: fixed;
      font-size:14px;
    }
    thead th{
      background:var(--head);
      color:#374151;
      text-align:left;
      font-weight:600;
      padding: 12px 12px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      white-space:nowrap;
    }
    tbody td{
      padding: 12px 12px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      vertical-align:top;
      color:#111827;
    }
    tbody tr:hover td{ background: var(--row-hover); }
    .muted{ color: var(--muted); font-size:13px; }
    .score{ font-weight:700; }
    .nowrap{ white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis; }
    .col-model{ width: 44%; }
    .col-ver{ width: 12%; }
    .col-metric{ width: 18%; }
    .col-score{ width: 10%; }
    .col-task{ width: 16%; }

    .footer{
      padding: 12px 18px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:12px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:13px;
    }
    .pager{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }
    .pageBtn{
      height:30px;
      min-width:30px;
      padding:0 10px;
      border:1px solid var(--border2);
      border-radius:6px;
      background:#fff;
      cursor:pointer;
      color:#374151;
    }
    .pageBtn[disabled]{
      opacity:.5; cursor:not-allowed;
    }
    .pageBtn.active{
      border-color: var(--link);
      color: var(--link);
      background: rgba(22,119,255,.06);
    }
    .goto{
      display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;
    }
    .goto input{
      height:30px; width:52px;
      border:1px solid var(--border2);
      border-radius:6px;
      padding:0 8px;
      outline:none;
    }
    .goto input:focus{
      border-color: var(--link);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--focus);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <h1 class="title">历史结果</h1>

        <div class="toolbar">
          <div class="field">
            <span>数据集：</span>
            <select id="dataset">
              <option value="aime2025" selected>aime2025</option>
              <option value="aime2024">aime2024</option>
              <option value="gsm8k">gsm8k</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="search" title="搜索模型名称">
            <!-- magnifier -->
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M10.5 18a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 0-15 7.5 7.5 0 0 1 0 15Z"
                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
              <path d="M16.3 16.3 21 21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <input id="kw" placeholder="搜索模型名称" autocomplete="off" />
            <button id="clearBtn" class="clearBtn" aria-label="clear">×</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tableWrap">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th class="col-model">模型名称</th>
              <th class="col-ver">数据集版本</th>
              <th class="col-metric">指标</th>
              <th class="col-score">得分</th>
              <th class="col-task">任务详情</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="tbody">
            <!-- rows injected by JS -->
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <div>
          共 <span id="total">0</span> 条
          <span class="muted">（示例：前端本地分页）</span>
        </div>

        <div class="pager">
          <button class="pageBtn" id="prev">‹</button>
          <div id="pages"></div>
          <button class="pageBtn" id="next">›</button>

          <div class="goto">
            <span>前往</span>
            <input id="goto" type="number" min="1" value="1" />
            <span>页</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<script>
  // 示例数据（可替换成你的真实数据）
  const data = [
    { model:"interns1-pro-candidate1-think-nosys-set1-temp0.8", ver:"bb832d", metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)", score:93.65, task:"api_eval_v3_3491" },
    { model:"interns1-pro-candidate6-think-nosys-set1",        ver:"bb832d", metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)", score:93.23, task:"api_eval_v3_3383" },
    { model:"interns1-pro-candidate1-think-nosys",             ver:"bb832d", metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)", score:93.12, task:"api_eval_v3_3548" },
    { model:"interns1-pro-candidate3-think-nosys",             ver:"bb832d", metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)", score:93.12, task:"api_eval_v3_3458" },
    { model:"interns1-pro-candidate5-think-nosys-set1",        ver:"bb832d", metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)", score:93.12, task:"api_eval_v3_3377" },
    { model:"interns1-pro-candidate5-think-nosys-set1",        ver:"bb832d", metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)", score:93.12, task:"api_eval_v3_3466" },
    { model:"interns1_mini_enhance_math_20251229rc20",         ver:"bb832d", metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)", score:92.40, task:"api_eval_v3_3658" },
    { model:"interns1_1_base02_20260110a_lr3e5_512gpu_fp8_thinking_aime2025_vers3",
                                                              ver:"bb832d", metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)", score:91.98, task:"api_eval_v3_2216" },
    // 多加一点方便看分页
    ...Array.from({length: 28}).map((_,i)=>({
      model:`interns1-pro-candidate${(i%6)+1}-think-nosys-run${i+1}`,
      ver:"bb832d",
      metric:"accuracy (32 runs average)",
      score:(91.5 + (i%10)*0.12).toFixed(2),
      task:`api_eval_v3_${3000+i}`
    }))
  ];

  const pageSize = 10;
  let page = 1;
  let keyword = "";

  const tbody = document.getElementById("tbody");
  const totalEl = document.getElementById("total");
  const kwEl = document.getElementById("kw");
  const clearBtn = document.getElementById("clearBtn");
  const pagesEl = document.getElementById("pages");
  const prevBtn = document.getElementById("prev");
  const nextBtn = document.getElementById("next");
  const gotoEl = document.getElementById("goto");

  function getFiltered(){
    const k = keyword.trim().toLowerCase();
    if(!k) return data;
    return data.filter(r => String(r.model).toLowerCase().includes(k));
  }

  function render(){
    const filtered = getFiltered();
    const total = filtered.length;
    totalEl.textContent = total;

    const totalPages = Math.max(1, Math.ceil(total / pageSize));
    page = Math.min(Math.max(1, page), totalPages);
    gotoEl.value = page;

    const start = (page - 1) * pageSize;
    const rows = filtered.slice(start, start + pageSize);

    tbody.innerHTML = rows.map(r => `
      <tr>
        <td class="nowrap" title="${escapeHtml(r.model)}">${escapeHtml(r.model)}</td>
        <td class="nowrap">${escapeHtml(r.ver)}</td>
        <td class="nowrap" title="${escapeHtml(r.metric)}">${escapeHtml(r.metric)}</td>
        <td class="score">${escapeHtml(String(r.score))}</td>
        <td class="nowrap"><a href="#" onclick="return false;">${escapeHtml(r.task)}</a></td>
      </tr>
    `).join("") || `<tr><td colspan="5" class="muted">无匹配结果</td></tr>`;

    // pager
    prevBtn.disabled = page <= 1;
    nextBtn.disabled = page >= totalPages;

    pagesEl.innerHTML = buildPageButtons(page, totalPages).map(p => {
      if (p === "...") return `<span class="muted" style="padding:0 6px">…</span>`;
      return `<button class="pageBtn ${p===page?'active':''}" data-p="${p}">${p}</button>`;
    }).join("");

    // clear button
    clearBtn.style.display = keyword ? "inline" : "none";
  }

  function buildPageButtons(current, total){
    // 简单省略策略：1 2 3 ... n
    if(total <= 7) return Array.from({length: total}, (_,i)=>i+1);
    const out = [1];
    if(current > 3) out.push("...");
    for(let p = Math.max(2, current-1); p <= Math.min(total-1, current+1); p++){
      out.push(p);
    }
    if(current < total-2) out.push("...");
    out.push(total);
    // 去重并保持顺序
    return out.filter((v,i,a)=> i===0 || v!==a[i-1]);
  }

  function escapeHtml(s){
    return String(s)
      .replaceAll("&","&amp;")
      .replaceAll("<","&lt;")
      .replaceAll(">","&gt;")
      .replaceAll('"',"&quot;")
      .replaceAll("'","&#39;");
  }

  // events
  kwEl.addEventListener("input", (e)=>{
    keyword = e.target.value;
    page = 1;
    render();
  });
  clearBtn.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
    keyword = "";
    kwEl.value = "";
    kwEl.focus();
    page = 1;
    render();
  });

  prevBtn.addEventListener("click", ()=>{ page--; render(); });
  nextBtn.addEventListener("click", ()=>{ page++; render(); });

  pagesEl.addEventListener("click", (e)=>{
    const btn = e.target.closest("button[data-p]");
    if(!btn) return;
    page = Number(btn.dataset.p);
    render();
  });

  gotoEl.addEventListener("change", ()=>{
    const filtered = getFiltered();
    const totalPages = Math.max(1, Math.ceil(filtered.length / pageSize));
    const v = Math.max(1, Math.min(totalPages, Number(gotoEl.value || 1)));
    page = v;
    render();
  });

  // dataset 切换仅演示：切换时清空搜索并回到第一页
  document.getElementById("dataset").addEventListener("change", ()=>{
    keyword = "";
    kwEl.value = "";
    page = 1;
    render();
  });

  render();
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

如果你希望它更贴近你截图：把搜索框放到“模型名称”表头里也行（但一般更推荐右上角）。你要哪种位置？我可以再给你对应的版本。

可以。你截图那种“表头里塞搜索框”的最佳替代就是：**用表格自带的列过滤器（filter dropdown）**，把搜索入口放到“模型名称”列标题右侧的小漏斗/筛选图标里，点开再输入关键字过滤。下面给你一个 Ant Design Table 的完整示例（可直接用）。

## Ant Design（React）列过滤器：模型名称可搜索
```jsx
import React, { useMemo, useRef, useState } from "react";
import { Table, Input, Button, Space, Typography } from "antd";
import { SearchOutlined } from "@ant-design/icons";

const { Link } = Typography;

const rawData = [
  {
    key: 1,
    model: "interns1-pro-candidate1-think-nosys-set1-temp0.8",
    ver: "bb832d",
    metric: "accuracy (32 runs average)",
    score: 93.65,
    task: "api_eval_v3_3491",
  },
  {
    key: 2,
    model: "interns1-pro-candidate6-think-nosys-set1",
    ver: "bb832d",
    metric: "accuracy (32 runs average)",
    score: 93.23,
    task: "api_eval_v3_3383",
  },
  // ...补充你的数据
];

export default function HistoryTable() {
  const [searchText, setSearchText] = useState("");
  const [searchedColumn, setSearchedColumn] = useState("");
  const searchInputRef = useRef(null);

  const columns = useMemo(() => {
    const getColumnSearchProps = (dataIndex, label = "搜索") => ({
      filterDropdown: ({ setSelectedKeys, selectedKeys, confirm, clearFilters, close }) => (
        <div style={{ padding: 8, width: 260 }}>
          <Input
            ref={searchInputRef}
            placeholder={`${label}`}
            value={selectedKeys[0]}
            onChange={(e) => setSelectedKeys(e.target.value ? [e.target.value] : [])}
            onPressEnter={() => {
              confirm();
              setSearchText(selectedKeys[0] || "");
              setSearchedColumn(dataIndex);
            }}
            allowClear
          />
          <Space style={{ marginTop: 8 }}>
            <Button
              type="primary"
              icon={<SearchOutlined />}
              size="small"
              onClick={() => {
                confirm();
                setSearchText(selectedKeys[0] || "");
                setSearchedColumn(dataIndex);
              }}
            >
              搜索
            </Button>
            <Button
              size="small"
              onClick={() => {
                clearFilters?.();
                setSearchText("");
                setSearchedColumn("");
                confirm({ closeDropdown: false });
              }}
            >
              重置
            </Button>
            <Button size="small" type="link" onClick={() => close()}>
              关闭
            </Button>
          </Space>
        </div>
      ),
      filterIcon: (filtered) => (
        <SearchOutlined style={{ color: filtered ? "#1677ff" : undefined }} />
      ),
      onFilter: (value, record) =>
        String(record[dataIndex] ?? "").toLowerCase().includes(String(value).toLowerCase()),
      onFilterDropdownOpenChange: (visible) => {
        if (visible) setTimeout(() => searchInputRef.current?.select(), 100);
      },
      render: (text) => text,
    });

    return [
      {
        title: "模型名称",
        dataIndex: "model",
        key: "model",
        ellipsis: true,
        ...getColumnSearchProps("model", "搜索模型名称"),
      },
      { title: "数据集版本", dataIndex: "ver", key: "ver", width: 120, ellipsis: true },
      { title: "指标", dataIndex: "metric", key: "metric", width: 220, ellipsis: true },
      { title: "得分", dataIndex: "score", key: "score", width: 100, sorter: (a, b) => a.score - b.score },
      {
        title: "任务详情",
        dataIndex: "task",
        key: "task",
        width: 160,
        render: (t) => <Link href="#" onClick={(e) => e.preventDefault()}>{t}</Link>,
      },
    ];
  }, []);

  return (
    <Table
      rowKey="key"
      columns={columns}
      dataSource={rawData}
      pagination={{ pageSize: 10 }}
    />
  );
}
```

### 你会得到的效果
- “模型名称”列标题右侧出现**筛选/搜索图标**
- 点开弹出一个小面板输入关键字
- 回车/点“搜索”后过滤该列数据
- 图标变蓝表示过滤生效

如果你不是 AntD（比如 Element Plus / ProTable / vxe-table），告诉我你用的表格组件，我给你对应的“列过滤器搜索”写法。

你这边要“预览效果”，我没法直接把页面跑起来给你看，但我可以给你一个**可直接在浏览器打开的单文件 HTML**，做出“表头筛选图标 → 下拉面板输入关键字 → 过滤模型名称列”的预览交互（不依赖 AntD）。你保存为 `preview.html` 双击打开即可看到效果。

```html
<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>列过滤器预览（模型名称）</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#fff; --page:#f3f4f6; --text:#111827; --muted:#6b7280;
      --border:#e5e7eb; --border2:#d9d9d9; --head:#f7f8fa;
      --link:#1677ff; --focus: rgba(22,119,255,.18);
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      --radius:10px; --radius-sm:8px;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{margin:0;background:var(--page);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,"PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei",Arial;}
    .page{max-width:1180px;margin:22px auto;padding:0 14px;}
    .card{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden}
    .header{padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
    .title{margin:0;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
    .tableWrap{overflow:auto}
    table{width:100%;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0;table-layout:fixed}
    thead th{
      background:var(--head);
      padding:12px 12px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      text-align:left;
      font-size:14px;
      color:#374151;
      font-weight:600;
      position:relative;
    }
    tbody td{
      padding:12px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      font-size:14px;color:var(--text);vertical-align:top;
      white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;
    }
    tbody tr:hover td{background:#fafafa}
    a{color:var(--link);text-decoration:none}
    a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
    .col-model{width:44%}
    .col-ver{width:12%}
    .col-metric{width:18%}
    .col-score{width:10%}
    .col-task{width:16%}

    /* 筛选图标按钮 */
    .thRow{
      display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    }
    .filterBtn{
      margin-left:6px;
      border:0; background:transparent; cursor:pointer;
      padding:4px; border-radius:6px;
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      color:#6b7280;
    }
    .filterBtn:hover{ background:#eef2ff; color:#374151; }
    .filterBtn.active{ color:var(--link); }
    .filterBtn:focus{ outline:none; box-shadow:0 0 0 2px var(--focus); }

    /* 下拉面板 */
    .dropdown{
      position:absolute;
      top: calc(100% + 8px);
      left: 8px;
      width: 280px;
      background:#fff;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding:10px;
      display:none;
      z-index: 50;
    }
    .dropdown.open{ display:block; }
    .dropdown .label{ font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:8px; }
    .dropdown input{
      width:100%; height:32px; padding:0 10px;
      border:1px solid var(--border2); border-radius:8px;
      outline:none; font-size:14px;
    }
    .dropdown input:focus{ border-color:var(--link); box-shadow:0 0 0 2px var(--focus); }
    .btnRow{ margin-top:10px; display:flex; gap:8px; }
    .btn{
      height:30px; padding:0 10px; border-radius:8px;
      border:1px solid var(--border2); background:#fff; cursor:pointer;
      font-size:13px; color:#374151;
    }
    .btn.primary{
      border-color: var(--link);
      background: var(--link);
      color:#fff;
    }
    .btn.link{
      border:0; background:transparent; color:var(--link);
    }

    .footer{
      padding: 12px 18px;
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;
      color:var(--muted); font-size:13px;
    }
    .pill{
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;
      border:1px dashed var(--border2);
      padding:6px 10px; border-radius:999px;
      background:#fff;
    }
    .x{
      border:0;background:transparent;cursor:pointer;color:#9ca3af;
      font-size:16px;line-height:1;padding:0 2px;
    }
  </style>
